text: A rare and remarkable opportunity to own over 5 pristine acres in the coveted town of Westlake, Texas. Tucked away in one of North Texas' most desirable enclaves, yet offering quick access to major highways, DFW International Airport, shopping, dining, and entertainment, this extraordinary parcel represents the perfect blend of privacy, elegance, and location. An exceptional investment in lifestyle and legacybring your architect, your dreams, and your vision to life on this premier piece of Westlake land.
